                                 README
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The example illustrates the communication between two components, and how TLM
classes can be used to create ports and exports to send data between the two.
ComponentB requests for data from ComponentA using the get() method via get_port
and ComponentA implements the get() method which was called by ComponentB. 
ComponentA creates a new packet and outputs the data to ComponentB.

      .------------------.                       .------------------.
      |   ComponentA     |Export ----------> Port|    ComponentB    |
      '------------------'                       '------------------'

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

